  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/2be5f77f61a80c932b9d8a6d493dd071.poster.avif?t=1765295426\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/2be5f77f61a80c932b9d8a6d493dd071.webm?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/2be5f77f61a80c932b9d8a6d493dd071.mp4?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/14bfeeb42c9b32dcd3b7633d257501a7.webp?t=1765295426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras_big/14bfeeb42c9b32dcd3b7633d257501a7.webp?t=1765295426 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/0b77964857ebff731fd5c03e0c814831.webp?t=1765295426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras_big/0b77964857ebff731fd5c03e0c814831.webp?t=1765295426 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Duck Detective is back! Get ready to interview suspects, inspect evidence, and deduce the truth in another stand-alone mystery!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/758f041eb594222f20b44d00bded2477.poster.avif?t=1765295426\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/758f041eb594222f20b44d00bded2477.webm?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/758f041eb594222f20b44d00bded2477.mp4?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/446bd5cbe7442c052b51d338cdbb60b5.webp?t=1765295426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras_big/446bd5cbe7442c052b51d338cdbb60b5.webp?t=1765295426 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This campsite might have ghosts, but the real thing haunting Eugene McQuacklin is his failed marriage and bread addiction. Can he escape the shadows of his past?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/285c418d071ea02e82317ec7f9a4db3b.poster.avif?t=1765295426\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/285c418d071ea02e82317ec7f9a4db3b.webm?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/285c418d071ea02e82317ec7f9a4db3b.mp4?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/cb28e8dc3a0ac84066ff5f217803a415.webp?t=1765295426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras_big/cb28e8dc3a0ac84066ff5f217803a415.webp?t=1765295426 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To the annoyance of the Duck Detective, he is joined by a new partner in (solving) crime. Work together to unravel the truth and nibble on the crumbs of justice!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/b6354222f52805fa332daa4115426b1f.webp?t=1765295426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras_big/b6354222f52805fa332daa4115426b1f.webp?t=1765295426 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 2-3 hour long cozy mystery game!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A stand-alone sequel to the acclaimed ‘Duck Detective: The Secret Salami!‘</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interview suspects, fill in the blanks and crack the case!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voice-acted cast of suspiciously secretive characters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a murky pond of delinquency and dredge up the truth!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw bread to the fine beak of lady justice!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/83693fd3534f547a1c70aad3bfaff2be.poster.avif?t=1765295426\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/83693fd3534f547a1c70aad3bfaff2be.webm?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/83693fd3534f547a1c70aad3bfaff2be.mp4?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/2be5f77f61a80c932b9d8a6d493dd071.poster.avif?t=1765295426\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/2be5f77f61a80c932b9d8a6d493dd071.webm?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/2be5f77f61a80c932b9d8a6d493dd071.mp4?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/14bfeeb42c9b32dcd3b7633d257501a7.webp?t=1765295426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras_big/14bfeeb42c9b32dcd3b7633d257501a7.webp?t=1765295426 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/0b77964857ebff731fd5c03e0c814831.webp?t=1765295426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras_big/0b77964857ebff731fd5c03e0c814831.webp?t=1765295426 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Duck Detective is back! Get ready to interview suspects, inspect evidence, and deduce the truth in another stand-alone mystery!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/758f041eb594222f20b44d00bded2477.poster.avif?t=1765295426\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/758f041eb594222f20b44d00bded2477.webm?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/758f041eb594222f20b44d00bded2477.mp4?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/446bd5cbe7442c052b51d338cdbb60b5.webp?t=1765295426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras_big/446bd5cbe7442c052b51d338cdbb60b5.webp?t=1765295426 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This campsite might have ghosts, but the real thing haunting Eugene McQuacklin is his failed marriage and bread addiction. Can he escape the shadows of his past?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/285c418d071ea02e82317ec7f9a4db3b.poster.avif?t=1765295426\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/285c418d071ea02e82317ec7f9a4db3b.webm?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/285c418d071ea02e82317ec7f9a4db3b.mp4?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/cb28e8dc3a0ac84066ff5f217803a415.webp?t=1765295426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras_big/cb28e8dc3a0ac84066ff5f217803a415.webp?t=1765295426 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To the annoyance of the Duck Detective, he is joined by a new partner in (solving) crime. Work together to unravel the truth and nibble on the crumbs of justice!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/b6354222f52805fa332daa4115426b1f.webp?t=1765295426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras_big/b6354222f52805fa332daa4115426b1f.webp?t=1765295426 width=800 height=41 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 2-3 hour long cozy mystery game!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A stand-alone sequel to the acclaimed ‘Duck Detective: The Secret Salami!‘</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interview suspects, fill in the blanks and crack the case!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voice-acted cast of suspiciously secretive characters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a murky pond of delinquency and dredge up the truth!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw bread to the fine beak of lady justice!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/83693fd3534f547a1c70aad3bfaff2be.poster.avif?t=1765295426\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/83693fd3534f547a1c70aad3bfaff2be.webm?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714620/extras/83693fd3534f547a1c70aad3bfaff2be.mp4?t=1765295426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
